00:02:12.300 --> 00:02:14.790
So there are two types of site maps.

49
00:02:15.210 --> 00:02:20.610
This is a flat site map and this is better suited for smaller to medium sized products.

50
00:02:20.610 --> 00:02:25.140
I'm thinking maybe like 10 to 100 pages, maybe even less.

51
00:02:25.140 --> 00:02:28.680
To be honest, there are four or less vertical levels.

