00:02:56.460 --> 00:02:58.320
they help house a lot of information.

60
00:02:58.320 --> 00:03:00.720
So we're talking like hundreds and hundreds of pages.

61
00:03:00.720 --> 00:03:06.420
We're talking maybe pages for like a government website, maybe like a huge e-commerce website.

