00:03:42.450 --> 00:03:47.250
It results in the creation of navigation hierarchies and categorizations of your product.

74
00:03:47.340 --> 00:03:49.590
You get a good understanding of your navigation.

75
00:03:49.590 --> 00:03:54.750
You can calculate the amount of content you need and it gives you a good understanding of your scope.

76
00:03:54.960 --> 00:03:57.840
So say maps are incredibly useful.

